data.description: WELCOME to this UBER Cute, One Story, WELL MAINTAINED Home!! SELLER WILLING TO PAY UP TO 5K IN CLOSING COSTS (with FULL PRICE offer ALSO - IF USING OUR PREF LENDER - 6% INT RATE!!!).  Fresh paint inside & out and solar screens in the front to provide privacy and nice curb appeal too! Large Family Rm open to Kitchen with ample counter space and OOODLES of cabinets!  Great for large family gatherings and FUN times!!  HUGE front BR with an oversized closet - middle BR great for a nursery, office or Yoga Room!!  Private Primary with an oversized, custom walk in shower!  Did I mention the great backyard with a SHED???
